---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Wildflour Café — Aro Valley, Wellington"
  description="Neighbourhood bakery-café in Aro Valley. Sourdough baked before sunrise, single-origin espresso, seasonal lunches."
  active="home"
>
  <main>
    <section class="hero">
      <p class="kicker">Aro Valley, Wellington</p>
      <h1>Baked before sunrise.<br />Gone by noon.</h1>
      <p class="lede">
        Wildflour is a small neighbourhood bakery-café. We mill heritage grains, ferment our
        sourdough slowly, and pull single-origin espresso — everything made in-house, every day.
      </p>
      <a class="cta" href="/menu">See today's menu</a>
    </section>

    <section class="features" aria-label="What we do">
      <article>
        <h2>Slow sourdough</h2>
        <p>
          Our loaves prove for 36 hours on stone-milled Canterbury flour. Crackly crust, custardy
          crumb — no shortcuts, no additives.
        </p>
      </article>
      <article>
        <h2>Serious coffee</h2>
        <p>
          A rotating single-origin espresso from Wellington roasters, dialled in every morning, plus
          a quiet filter list for the patient.
        </p>
      </article>
      <article>
        <h2>Seasonal cabinet</h2>
        <p>
          Cardamom knots, seasonal galettes, and a savoury pie of the week — the cabinet follows the
          market, not the other way round.
        </p>
      </article>
    </section>

    <section id="story" class="story">
      <h2>Our story</h2>
      <p>
        Wildflour started as a Saturday market stall in 2022 — one bench, one oven, and a queue we
        never expected. Two years later we took over the old dairy on Aro Street and never looked
        back. We bake for our neighbours first: the shelves are stocked for the morning rush, and
        when it's gone, it's gone.
      </p>
      <p>
        We keep things small on purpose. One bake a day, a menu that fits on a chalkboard, and
        coffee made by people who know your order before you reach the counter.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section id="visit" class="visit">
      <h2>Visit us</h2>
      <p>
        You'll find us at <strong>14 Aro Street, Aro Valley, Wellington</strong> — look for the
        terracotta awning. Come early for the full cabinet; the sourdough rarely makes it past
        lunchtime.
      </p>
      <p>
        Questions, wholesale, or a very large cake? Email
        <a href="mailto:hello@wildflourcafe.nz">hello@wildflourcafe.nz</a>.
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>
</Base>

<style>
  .hero {
    padding: clamp(3rem, 10vw, 6rem) 0 3rem;
    max-width: 44rem;
  }
  .kicker {
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--terracotta-deep);
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }
  .hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 6vw, 3.6rem);
  }
  .lede {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    max-width: 38rem;
  }
  .cta {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    background: var(--terracotta);
    color: #fff;
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .cta:hover {
    background: var(--terracotta-deep);
  }
  .features {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(15rem, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    padding: 2rem 0;
  }
  .features article {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid var(--flour);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }
  .features h2 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
  }
  .story,
  .visit {
    padding: 2.5rem 0 0;
    max-width: 44rem;
  }
</style>
